{
    "version": "0.17.4",
    "description": "小狼毫输入法 - 一个模块化、可扩展且可定制的输入法引擎 | A modular, extensible, and customizable input method engine.",
    "homepage": "https://rime.im/",
    "license": {
        "identifier": "GPL-3.0-only",
        "url": "https://github.com/rime/weasel/blob/master/LICENSE.txt"
    },
    "suggest": {
        "input-schemes": [
            "abyss/amzxyz.rime_wanxiang",
            "abyss/iDvel.rime-ice"
        ],
        "model": "abyss/amzxyz.rime_wanxiang.model"
    },
    "notes": [
        "The installation directory: $env:ProgramFiles\\Rime",
        "Refer to: https://abyss.abgox.com/faq/external-installation-directory",
        " ",
        "You can install an input scheme to get started quickly.",
        "  - Wanxiang Pinyin: abyss/amzxyz.rime_wanxiang",
        "  - Ice Pinyin: abyss/iDvel.rime-ice",
        "You can install the Wanxiang syntax model: abyss/amzxyz.rime_wanxiang.model"
    ],
    "notes-cn": [
        "安装目录: $env:ProgramFiles\\Rime",
        "参考: https://abyss.abgox.com/faq/external-installation-directory",
        " ",
        "你可以直接安装一种输入方案以快速上手",
        "  - 万象拼音输入方案: abyss/amzxyz.rime_wanxiang",
        "  - 雾凇拼音输入方案: abyss/iDvel.rime-ice",
        "你可以安装万象语法模型: abyss/amzxyz.rime_wanxiang.model"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://github.com/rime/weasel/releases/download/0.17.4/weasel-0.17.4.0-installer.exe",
            "hash": "cf509534a8f5f8af9c98ed7cbb8f135439f145a8cbe7e50ede42bb5b5ab45c29"
        },
        "arm64": {
            "url": "https://github.com/rime/weasel/releases/download/0.17.4/weasel-0.17.4.0-installer.exe",
            "hash": "cf509534a8f5f8af9c98ed7cbb8f135439f145a8cbe7e50ede42bb5b5ab45c29"
        }
    },
    "pre_install": [
        "$bucket = if ($bucket) { $bucket } else { (scoop config).'abgox-abyss-bucket-name' }",
        ". $bucketsdir\\$bucket\\script\\utils.ps1",
        "A-Start-Install",
        "A-Require-Admin",
        "$Uninstaller = \"$env:ProgramFiles\\Rime\\weasel-$version\\uninstall.exe\"",
        "if (Test-Path $Uninstaller) { A-Uninstall-Exe -Uninstaller $Uninstaller }",
        "A-New-LinkDirectory \"$env:AppData\\Rime\"",
        "A-Install-Exe -Uninstaller $Uninstaller"
    ],
    "post_install": [
        "$bucket = if ($bucket) { $bucket } else { (scoop config).'abgox-abyss-bucket-name' }",
        ". $bucketsdir\\$bucket\\script\\utils.ps1",
        "A-Complete-Install"
    ],
    "pre_uninstall": [
        "$bucket = if ($bucket) { $bucket } else { (scoop config).'abgox-abyss-bucket-name' }",
        ". $bucketsdir\\$bucket\\script\\utils.ps1",
        "A-Start-Uninstall",
        "A-Require-Admin",
        "A-Uninstall-Exe",
        "A-Remove-Link"
    ],
    "post_uninstall": [
        "$bucket = if ($bucket) { $bucket } else { (scoop config).'abgox-abyss-bucket-name' }",
        ". $bucketsdir\\$bucket\\script\\utils.ps1",
        "A-Complete-Uninstall"
    ],
    "checkver": {
        "script": [
            ". $pwd\\script\\utils.ps1",
            "A-Get-VersionFromGithubAPI"
        ],
        "regex": "(.+)"
    },
    "autoupdate": {
        "architecture": {
            "64bit": {
                "url": "https://github.com/rime/weasel/releases/download/$version/weasel-$version.0-installer.exe"
            },
            "arm64": {
                "url": "https://github.com/rime/weasel/releases/download/$version/weasel-$version.0-installer.exe"
            }
        },
        "hash": {
            "mode": "github"
        }
    }
}
